{"tid":2390212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約十輛小巴慢駛遊行　促放寬防疫措施振經濟","createTime":"2021-02-01T11:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T15:02:41.000Z","uid":291865,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a05969d7edb0a9e97fdd709aae26f865abb44ef7","tid":2390212,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"約十輛小巴慢駛遊行 促放寬防疫措施振經濟<br />\n4分鐘前<br />\n【Now新聞台】有團體發起小巴慢駛遊行，促請政府放寬防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n復興經濟民生大聯盟約十架紅色小巴貼上標語，由旺角出發，沿彌敦道慢駛遊行，過海前往政府總部，抗議政府的防疫措施，令到各行各業經營困難，要求政府在目前疫情受控下，考慮於農曆年前放寬限聚令等防疫措施，恢復經濟活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=422547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422547&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=60fb06d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422547&h=72c0221c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=422547</a>"},{"pid":"b9845fd1024f54d292d7e7a737fa122f62f2bd15","tid":2390212,"uid":76603,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:50:44.000Z","msg":"用國安法拉晒佢哋"},{"pid":"65383d0a1c224ded1c3fc28b3eac74b798c3de01","tid":2390212,"uid":57255,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:50:48.000Z","msg":"嘩好撚激進呀屌你老味，咁激既個政府一定會聽你講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230cf77743f150e918fb63463f8e366aaeadd3e0","tid":2390212,"uid":76609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:52:15.000Z","msg":"整路障唔使坐半年？"},{"pid":"bd7da0a5163ec17ea43adb0ac37460abf46f1dc9","tid":2390212,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"230cf77743f150e918fb63463f8e366aaeadd3e0","tid":2390212,"uid":76609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:52:15.000Z","msg":"整路障唔使坐半年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:52:46.000Z","msg":"